(46, 4, '<IMG Src="fll_42.jpg" Width=500><BR>\r\nTimova fotka.<BR>&nbsp;<BR>\r\n\r\n<P>\r\nNa kruzku vo stvrtok sa nam velmi nedarilo, preto sme robota dokoncili az doma.\r\nNa prvy pokus nam to hadzalo vsetky gulicky na jedno miesto ale po miernych \r\nupravach v programe nam to celkom dobre fungovalo. Tu je video:<BR>\r\n<P Align="center">\r\n\r\n<object width="640" height="360"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/h3VZzUNK91c?hl=en_US&amp;version=3"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/h3VZzUNK91c?hl=en_US&amp;version=3" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="640" height="360" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>\r\n<BR>&nbsp;<BR>\r\nA toto je program:<BR>\r\n<IMG Src="fll_45.png"><BR>&nbsp;<BR>\r\n\r\n<IMG Src="fll_46.png"><BR>&nbsp;<BR>\r\n<A HREF="fll_47.rbt">fll_47.rbt</A>, <A HREF="Blok.rbt">Blok.rbt</A>\r\n\r\n<BR>&nbsp;<BR><BR>&nbsp;<BR><BR>&nbsp;<BR>\r\n\r\nDalsi clenovia timu vsak tiez vymysleli jedno riesenie. Ale kedze NXT nemali\r\ndoma, vymysleli to takto - video nasho riesenia:<BR>\r\n<object width="480" height="360"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/SJcEJXZNf5U?version=3&amp;hl=en_US"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/SJcEJXZNf5U?version=3&amp;hl=en_US" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="480" height="360" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true"></embed></object>\r\n<BR>&nbsp;<BR><BR>&nbsp;<BR>\r\n<IMG Src="fll_43.jpg" Width=500><BR>\r\nHotovo:<BR>&nbsp;<BR> \r\n<IMG Src="fll_41.gif"><BR>\r\n\r\nProgram v Scratchi<BR>', 0),
