mily:"Calibri","sans-serif";\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-fareast-language:EN-US;}\n</style>\n<![endif]--></p>\n<p>Mili organizatori letnej ligy,</p>\n<p>posielame vam riesenie piatej ulohy - umenie.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Pri navrhu konstrukcie robota sme mysleli na:</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - &nbsp; </span></span></span>Kresliace pero presne v&nbsp;osi otacania kolies</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; </span></span></span>Pohon kolies pomocou snekov pre presny pohyb robota</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; </span></span></span>Posun kresliaceho pera presne zvisle</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - &nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Podla touch senzorov vieme kedy je pero hore alebo dole</p>\n<p>Robot pomocou maleho motora dava pero dole alebo hore a&nbsp;pomocou velkych<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>motorov sa pohybuje.</p>\n<p>Ev3 program ponuka nasledovne myBlocks, pomocou ktorych je mozne nakreslit lubovolny obrazok:</p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Chod_rovno</p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Otoc_sa_namieste</p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Kresli_obluk</p>\n<p>Naprogramovat myBlock Kresli_obluk bolo velmi narocne. Sme radi, ze nam s&nbsp;tym trener pomohol.</p>\n<p>Ako video ukazky posielame videa, ako robot kresli nasledovne obrazky:</p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Domcek</p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Smajlika</p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Logo OliSeb nasho timu</p>\n<p>Zial este nevieme strihat a&nbsp;upravovat videa, a&nbsp;v&nbsp;kratkosti casu sme sa to nestihli naucit.</p>\n<p>Ak chcete vidiet hned vysledok, kludne preskocte vsetko az na koniec.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">V&nbsp;prilohach posielame:</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - &nbsp; </span></span></span><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">Fotku robota </strong></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - &nbsp; </span></span></span>Ev3 program</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>YouTube link (<a href="http://youtu.be/OMtsnQ0rodo" target="_blank">http://youtu.be/OMtsnQ0rodo</a>, <a href="http://youtu.be/vdT1QaIU88I" target="_blank">http://youtu.be/vdT1QaIU88I</a> a https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UUbhPH3Zo_w&nbsp; )</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Tesime sa na dalsie ulohy!</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Oliver, Sebi, Adam</p>', 0),
(226, 25, '<p>Chceli sme spraviť robota, ktor&yacute; by vedel maľovať obrazy. Minule sme č&iacute;tali, že obraz Jacksona Pollocka bol vydražen&yacute; ako najdrah&scaron;&iacute; na svete, tak sme chceli spraviť niečo podobn&eacute; :)</p>\n<p><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jackson_Pollock#/media/File:No._5,_1948.jpg" target="_blank">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jackson_Pollock#/media/File:No._5,_1948.jpg</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Kon&scaron;trukcia:</strong></p>\n<p>Na robota sme použili 2 motory. Jedn&yacute;m sa pohybuje dopredu a dozadu a druh&yacute;m h&yacute;be ramenom. Použili sme aj 2 tlakov&eacute; senzory-pomocou nich robot vie, že už je na konci a tak zmen&iacute; smer. Zapojen&yacute; je aj ultrazvukov&yacute; senzor a podľa neho robot vie, že či m&aacute; rameno pohybovať viac vľavo, v strede alebo vpravo. Ak nie je pred senzorom, nič, tak sa pohybuje rameno po celej &scaron;&iacute;rke.</p>\n<p><strong>Program:</strong></p>\n<p>Robot vie kresliť obrazy aj &uacute;plne s&aacute;m - pohyby dopredu a dozadu s&uacute; preto spraven&eacute;&nbsp; n&aacute;hodnou r&yacute;chlosťou na n&aacute;hodne určen&yacute; čas. Ak ubehne dan&yacute; čas a robot e&scaron;te nie je na konci, tak znova vzgeneruje n&aacute;hodn&uacute; r&yacute;chlosť a n&aacute;hodn&yacute; čas.</p>\n<p>Popri pohybe dopredu a dozadu k&yacute;ve ramenom na ktorom m&aacute; farbičku alebo fixku. Vždy rameno n&aacute;hodne vych&yacute;li a trochu tam zafarb&iacute;. Ak nie je nič pred ultrazvukov&yacute;m senzorom, tak rameno chod&iacute; n&aacute;hodne po celej &scaron;&iacute;rke, inak iba vľavo, v strede alebo vpravo podľa toho, ako bl&iacute;zko je niečo pred senzorom.</p>\n<p>Obraz je možn&eacute; kresliť buď celkom automaticky alebo aj umelec do toho m&ocirc;že zasahovať t&yacute;m, že buď stlač&iacute; tlakov&yacute; senzor sk&ocirc;r než pr&iacute;de na koniec alebo pomocou ultrazvukov&eacute;ho senzora m&ocirc;že meniť, v ktorej časti bude chodiť farbička.</p>\n<p><strong>Princ&iacute;p uchytenia farbičky:</strong></p>\n<p>Chceli sme, aby sa dali použiť r&ocirc;zne farbičky, preto sme vysk&uacute;&scaron;ali r&ocirc;zne verzie uchytenia (s&uacute; na poslednej fotke). Prv&eacute; uchytenie nebolo veľmi stabiln&eacute; a bolo iba na jeden druh farbičky. Druh&eacute; už vedelo uchytiť r&ocirc;zne farbičky, ale st&aacute;le nebolo veľmi pevn&eacute;. Až to, ktor&eacute; je na videu spoľahlivo udržalo r&ocirc;zne veľkosti farbičiek.</p>', 0),
(227, 25, '<p>V tomto kole umenia, sme sa rozhodli urobiť tlačiareň.</p>\n<p>Na&scaron;a tlačiareň vyrobila obr&aacute;zky, z ktor&yacute;ch sa n&aacute;m podarilo natočiť dva (žial &scaron;kola bola v piatok zatvoren&aacute;). Jeden obr&aacute;zok je logo EV3 (t&uacute;to stavebnicu by sme nejak&yacute;m sp&ocirc;osbom chceli z&iacute;skať :) ) a druh&yacute; obr&aacute;zok je obdĺžnik.</p>\n<p>Program funguje na z&aacute;klade pos&uacute;vania ramena pera a to horizont&aacute;lne a vertik&aacute;lne, a z&aacute;roveň pos&uacute;van&iacute;m papiera.</p>', 0),
(228, 25, '<p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm">Dobr&yacute; deň v&aacute;žen&aacute; porota!</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm">TS Team V&aacute;m op&auml;ť zasiela svoje rie&scaron;enie &uacute;lohy č. 5 &ndash; UMENIE.&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm">Pri navrhovan&iacute; robota, niektor&iacute; z&nbsp;n&aacute;s, mali dobr&yacute; n&aacute;pad využiť pohybliv&uacute; časť z&nbsp;robota z&nbsp;CERNu. Vznikol robot s&nbsp;p&aacute;som, ktor&yacute; sme využili na &bdquo;bodkovan&yacute; obr&aacute;zok&ldquo; a&nbsp;aj na bonus. Tento robot pracuje ako ploter a&nbsp;na p&aacute;sov&uacute; časť sa m&ocirc;žu prip&aacute;jať r&ocirc;zne nadstavce. Pri umiestňovan&iacute; slnka, mot&yacute;ľov a&nbsp;kvetov sme využili posun p&aacute;su s&nbsp;n&aacute;kladom zvrchu.</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm">Ďal&scaron;&iacute; robot sme využili&nbsp;pri v&yacute;robe z&aacute;kladu pre umeleck&yacute; a&nbsp;&uacute;žitkov&yacute; v&yacute;robok &ndash; &scaron;perk, ktor&yacute; skompletizovala jedin&aacute; členka n&aacute;&scaron;ho t&iacute;mu. Prv&yacute; large motor zabezpečoval pohyb dopredu a&nbsp;dozadu, druh&yacute; large vys&uacute;val cel&yacute; držiak medium motora, ktor&yacute; robil ot&aacute;čanie guličky. Tohto robota sme chceli využiť aj na maľovanie vaj&iacute;čka s&nbsp;využit&iacute;m viacer&yacute;ch &scaron;tetcov, s&nbsp;viacer&yacute;mi farbami, no z&nbsp;časov&eacute;ho d&ocirc;vodu sme to nestihli &ndash; možno inokedy. Na fotke je vidieť, že sme mali pripraven&uacute; aj 3D &uacute;pravu vianočnej gule &ndash; testovanie p&aacute;jky fungovalo, nestihli sme farbenie.</p>\n<p style="margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:10.0pt;margin-left:\n0cm"><strong>&Scaron;PECI&Aacute;LNY BONUS: </strong>Na&scaron;im dne&scaron;n&yacute;m bonusom je samostatn&yacute; v&yacute;tvor n&aacute;&scaron;ho najmlad&scaron;ieho člena t&iacute;mu, ktor&yacute; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">m&aacute; iba 7 rokov</span>. S&aacute;m si robota naprogramoval a zostrihal video. D&iacute;ky Ri&scaron;ko!</p>\n<p style="margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt">Prajeme V&aacute;m kr&aacute;sny umeleck&yacute; z&aacute;žitok.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-ansi-language:\nSK;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">TS Team</span></p>', 0);
