mily:"Calibri","sans-serif";\n	mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\n	mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\n	mso-fareast-language:EN-US;}\n</style>\n<![endif]--></p>\n<p>Mili organizatori letnej ligy,</p>\n<p>posielame vam riesenie ulohy &ndash; 6. ulohy <span style="color: #1f497d;">FLL@home</span>.</p>\n<p>Nas robot najprv pomocou senzora najde predmet a&nbsp;podla farby vie, ci je to flasa alebo pohar. Potom hlada a najde druhy predmet a&nbsp;urobi to iste. Potom pride k&nbsp;flasi, zoberie ju a&nbsp;odnesie k&nbsp;poharu. Nakoniec vodu do pohara naleje.</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">V&nbsp;prilohach posielame:</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Fotky robota</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>Ev3 program</p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span>YouTube link (<a href="http://youtu.be/VScIuaTQd0w" target="_blank">http://youtu.be/VScIuaTQd0w</a>) a (<a href="http://youtu.be/uoZ-9ubvekM" target="_blank">http://youtu.be/uoZ-9ubvekM</a>)</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Tesime sa na dalsie ulohy!</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal">Oliver, Sebi, Adam</p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi;">&nbsp;</span></p>', 0),
(240, 26, '<p><span style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;">Robot využ&iacute;va 4 motory a jeden piest. Z toho dva motory sa zap&aacute;jaj&uacute; do jedn&eacute;ho portu A. Dva motory využ&iacute;va na pohyb robota, ďal&scaron;ie 2 motory - zapojen&eacute; do jedn&eacute;ho portu použ&iacute;va na naklopenie fľa&scaron;e potrebn&eacute;ho na naliatie vody do poh&aacute;ra. Na zabezpečenie v&auml;č&scaron;ej stability pri nakl&aacute;pan&iacute; fľa&scaron;e sme použili 2 &scaron;nekov&eacute; prevodovky. Na pritlačenie a pridrženie fľa&scaron;e o sklopn&eacute; rameno je využit&yacute; piest, ktor&yacute; sa zap&iacute;na pohybom motora na naklopenie ramena. Na hľadanie fľa&scaron;e a poh&aacute;ra s&uacute; využit&eacute; 2 sn&iacute;mače vzdialenosti.</span></p>', 0),
(241, 26, '<p>Najprv sme museli vymyslieť ako bude ten robot bude fungovať. A&nbsp;po čase ako sme ho stavali tak nastalo p&aacute;r celkom z&aacute;važn&yacute;ch probl&eacute;mov, ktor&eacute; sme museli vyrie&scaron;iť. Jeden z&nbsp;nich bolo umiestnenie ramena a&nbsp;dobr&eacute; rozloženie v&aacute;hy. Z&aacute;klad robota tvor&iacute; jeden veľk&yacute; motor, ktor&yacute; m&aacute; na starosti pohyb robota. Tak tiež veľmi d&ocirc;ležit&aacute; časť je rameno, ktor&eacute;ho z&aacute;klad tvor&iacute; jeden veľk&yacute; a jeden mal&yacute; motor. Veľk&yacute; motor ot&aacute;ča cel&yacute;m mechanizmom, ktor&yacute; vyleje obsah fľa&scaron;ky do poh&aacute;ra a&nbsp;pevn&eacute; uchytenie fľa&scaron;ky zabezpečuje mal&yacute; motor zo svojimi robotick&yacute;mi ručičkami. Aby robot zastal pred fľa&scaron;kou, tak je na ramene priroben&yacute; ultrazvukov&yacute; senzor, ktor&yacute; je nadstaven&yacute; aby zastal pred fľa&scaron;kou. Podobn&uacute; časť &uacute;lohy zohr&aacute;va aj farebn&yacute; senzor, ktor&yacute; m&aacute; za &uacute;lohu včasn&eacute; zastavenie pred poh&aacute;rom.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="right">Ďakujeme za pozornosť</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="right">aj za bod&iacute;ky</p>', 0),
(242, 26, '<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: ''Calibri Light'', sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">N&aacute;&scaron; program pomocou infračerven&eacute;ho senzora najprv n&aacute;jde objekt. Potom pomocou farebn&eacute;ho senzora urč&iacute; či je to fľa&scaron;ka(čierna), alebo poh&aacute;r(žlt&yacute;). Ak je to fľa&scaron;ka&nbsp;</span>zoberie ju a&nbsp;naleje do poh&aacute;ra. Ak to je poh&aacute;r hľad&aacute; ďalej fľa&scaron;ku, ktor&uacute; n&aacute;sledne vyleje do poh&aacute;ra. Zdv&iacute;hanie a otv&aacute;ranie ruky je ovl&aacute;dan&eacute; pomocou jedn&eacute;ho medium motora, na obr&aacute;zku si m&ocirc;žete v&scaron;imn&uacute;ť mechanizmus, ktor&yacute; najprv&nbsp;ruku zavrie a&nbsp;potom mierne nadvihne. Ot&aacute;čanie ruky je roben&eacute; mocou ďal&scaron;ieho medium motora a&nbsp;pohyb robota zabezpečuj&uacute; dva large motory. Na presn&eacute; ot&aacute;čanie e&scaron;te použ&iacute;vame gyro senzor a&nbsp;cel&uacute; &uacute;lohu sp&uacute;&scaron;ťame touch senzorom.</p>', 0),
(243, 26, '<p>...</p>', 0);
