p>\n<p><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>Mili organizatori letnej ligy,</p>\n<p>posielame vam riesenie 7. ulohy <span style="color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;">S</span><span style="color: black;">lalom</span>.</p>\n<p>Robot rozoznava flasky <span style="color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;">pomocou</span> ultrazvuko<span style="color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">veho</span> senzor<span style="color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">u</span>.</p>\n<p>Najviac nam dalo zabrat ladenie modulu otoc<span style="color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">_</span>sa<span style="color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">_</span>okolo<span style="color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">_</span>kolky (flasky) ale nakoniec sme to zvladl<span style="color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">i</span>.</p>\n<p><span style="color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">Zistili sme, ze ultrazvukovy senzor v&nbsp;niektorych pripadoch nieco v miestnosti rusilo. Museli sme slalomovu drahu umiestnit v&nbsp;miestnosti inak, a&nbsp;potom nam to uz fungovalo. Tu su casy dosiahnute nasim robotom:</span></p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin; color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">1.<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: ''Calibri'',''sans-serif''; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #1f497d; mso-themecolor: dark2;">Povinna Jazda: <span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>34,766 s</span></p>\n<p style="margin-left: 36.0pt; text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2;"><span