p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">Mili organizatori letnej ligy,</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">posielame vam riesenie ulohy &ndash; 8. ulohy <span style="color: black;">Tri orechy.</span></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; color: black;">Nas robot chodi hore &ndash; dolu a&nbsp;hlada orechy. Ked mu nejaky vhupne do "priecinku" tak ho zbada, zaklapne zalapku, aby sa orech nesuchal po zemi a&nbsp;podla svetla sa vrati do zakladne. Pri toceni videa sme nevedeli najst treti orech, a&nbsp;tak sme namiesto orechu pouzili rajcinu (ako vidiet na videu).</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">V&nbsp;prilohach posielame:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">Fotky robota </span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">Ev3 program</span></p>\n<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">-<span style="font: 7.0pt ''Times New Roman'';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">YouTube linky (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vx5uRNph4lQ">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vx5uRNph4lQ</a>),( <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TrJQOjcf_us">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TrJQOjcf_us</a>) a (</span><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;"><a href="http://youtu.be/gSn0TM5_A7I" target="_blank">http://youtu.be/gSn0TM5_A7I</a>)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">Tesime sa na dalsie ulohy!</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">Oliver, Sebi, Adam<br /></span></p>', 0),
(271, 28, '<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">Dobr&yacute; deň v&scaron;etk&yacute;m!</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">TS Team V&aacute;m zasiela svoje rie&scaron;enie 8. &uacute;lohy &ndash; Tri orie&scaron;ky.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">Pri rie&scaron;en&iacute; tejto &uacute;lohy sme zostrojili robota, ktor&yacute; na naberanie orie&scaron;kov použ&iacute;va posuv zar&aacute;žky, ktor&aacute; je pripevnen&aacute; na p&aacute;se. Posuv p&aacute;su zabezpečuje jeden large motor, ďal&scaron;ie dva s&uacute; určen&eacute; na pohyb robota. Po nabrat&iacute; je orie&scaron;ok posunut&yacute; na zbern&uacute; plo&scaron;inu, ktor&aacute; je medzi kolesami v&nbsp;spodnej časti robota.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">Najv&auml;č&scaron;&iacute; probl&eacute;m bol pre n&aacute;s n&aacute;jsť orie&scaron;ok v&nbsp;predp&iacute;sanej ploche &ndash; bohužiaľ ultrazvukov&yacute; senzor neposl&uacute;chal - asi mu vadila veľkosť a&nbsp;obl&yacute; tvar orechov, tak sme si vymysleli ich krabičkov&eacute; kryty, ktor&eacute; sme po zameran&iacute; prek&aacute;žky z&nbsp;orecha odstr&aacute;nili.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">Na&scaron;a predstava bola nasledovn&aacute;: robot sa pomaly ot&aacute;ča nasmerovan&yacute; na hern&uacute; plochu a&nbsp;m&aacute; zadan&uacute; podmienku: ak n&aacute;jde&scaron; predmet do vzdialenosti 1m /uhlopriečka/ choď ku nemu. Nasledovať mala korekcia pohybu, aby bol robot zbernou časťou pred orie&scaron;kom. Zberanie ostan&yacute;ch orie&scaron;kov malo nasledovať hneď, nakoľko m&aacute;me zbern&eacute; miesto dostatočn&eacute; pre viac orechov.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">Color senzor sme umiestnili vo vodorovnej polohe v&nbsp;prednej časti robota a&nbsp;sl&uacute;ži na vr&aacute;tenie robota do domčeka - kde svieti svetlo.</span></p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10.0pt 0cm;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">Ďakujeme TS Team</span></p>', 0),
